lead_paragraph: The weather gods gave West Indies a lifeline in their quest to avoid defeat in the second test against India when rain washed out the final session of day three in Kingston, Jamaica on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Rain Gives West Indies Lifeline Against Dominant India
